item.title: Coach Dave Thomas
item.description: There is great happiness in the lifelong pursuit of human potential.”-Coach David Thomas Dave Thomas of Seattle, WA is founding coach at Austin Jiu-Jitsu. While Dave now trains and works in Seattle, he is proud to have built Austin Jiu-Jitsu from a small group of friends in his garage to a thriving community of dedicated students from 2003 - 2017. He visits the gym when traveling to Austin to roll with his students and friends.
